==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cicisbeo
<hw>Ci`cis*be"o</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
It. <plw>Cicisbei</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[It.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A professed admirer of a married woman; a dangler about
women.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A knot of silk or ribbon attached to a fan, walking
stick, etc.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ciclatoun</ent>⟦br⟧
